Life lately 💙

It’s about to be the busy season here again, and I can’t wait to get back in the full swing of gigs. I’ve been focused on writing music, financial intelligence, taking care of/exercising my body, reading my Bible and Devotion daily, and of course, the health and happiness of my relationships with friends, and mostly with Jessica. 💙 

To say my decision to move back to 30A was a good thing for me would be an major understatement. I could not feel better about the path and the blessing of this life that God has given me.

Cheers to new beginnings 🥰

Probably looking for someone to crack my back😮‍💨😫iykyk😂

Hey Siri, play The Dress by Dijon #mood
What’s cooler than 24? Getting engaged before 25💍💙🧽

I can’t believe it’s almost been a month since our special day 💙 

I wanted to take the time to say “Thank You” to a handful of people that made this day possible.

First off, we want to give a HUGE thank you to @oldfloridafishhouse and @coastside30a (especially the owners, Keith and Tammie) for making this day possible. From helping me pick out the perfect proposal spot, to opening your venue to us for the surprise engagement party, and even to the smallest of things like convincing Jessica to get her nails done for a “wine shoot”, this day would not have been possible without y’all. Old Florida has not only given me a space to share my music from the very beginning, but now are even MORE a part of the happiest parts of Jessica and I’s story to together. I love you guys 💙

Next we wanted to thank @jesseme93 for being the best of friends and capturing this special moment in the most stunning way, as well as to @briebenefit and @kemperturner helping me plan the proposal all along the way. This was a tall task and extremely stressful, and I truly couldn’t have done it without y’all. We couldn’t be more grateful to have y’all in our lives in such an intimate way. 

And last, but not least, to our family and friends who made the trip to be there on such a special day and to celebrate the love we have found in each other. Jessica and I would both agree that we are blessed beyond measure by having such an incredible support network of people in our lives. We love you all 💙

Here is to forever, babe @jessicalarson335
Cigars to celebrate a great next year of life ahead 💙 Feeling grateful today.

A belated “Dirty 30” post for my best-worst friends birthday!🤗 I can’t believe you’re already 30, that’s so cringe honestly 💙🤪

ONLY HUMAN - Episode Five: Jared Herzog

Based off a project that originally started as a photo series on instagram (@onlyhumanimages), ONLY HUMAN expands the series to a set of documentary films exclusively for social media.

From models, social media stars, to singers and public speakers, season one will take you behind the scenes and into the lives of five widely recognized individuals as they tell stories never shared anywhere until now.

Warning: Objects in mirror are closer than they appear 🫶🏽

Happy new year, and thank you so much to everyone who came out to the show last night. I had SUCH a blast playing @hoteleffie with the boys last night for the NYE event! Here are a few shots @jesseme93 snagged.

Here is to 2024 🫶🏽💙

We don’t always have the luxury to determine how life changes, but we certainly have the ability to control how we allow them to change us. 

In 2024, I vow to be more devoted to my creativity. I vow to be more faithful to the wonderful opportunities I am presented with big or small. And I vow to make the most of what I’ve been given in this life. 

2023 ended in a way I would’ve never expected it to. I wanted to take a moment to thank everyone who has been in my corner or come to me with wisdom on their lips and love in their hearts. I am doing well. And I will be doing even better.

I am currently in the air flying to Australia for the next 2 weeks, which I am PUMPED about (shoutout @bentemby for making it happen). When I return, I fully intend to put my best foot forward and be more faithful on this platform with my music as well.

One last shoutout to @jesseme93 for these photos we took before the new year. These were taken just days after things were broken off, and it was one of the first times I had left the house to see a friend. He is a really good one and a very creative/talented one at that.

I’ll see you all soon 🫶🏽
30A Based Singer-Songwriter 💙
